TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTCOMP, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTAGT, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTTYPE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDAGYCODE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWAGYCODE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDAGYCLASS, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWAGYCLASS, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDAGYNAME, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWAGYNAME, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDDISTRICT, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWDISTRICT, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDDMCODE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWDMCODE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDDMCLASS, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWDMCLASS, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTOLDDMNAME, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTNEWDMNAME, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.DTEEFFECTIVEDATE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTREMARKS, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTLASTUPDATE, IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.DTELASTUPDATE, 1 AS TXTGROUP , IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.TXTSTATUS FROM IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP WHERE IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP.txtGroup IN( SELECT MAX( txtGroup ) FROM IN_PI_AOR_SETUP_TEMP )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 1 DEC_RUNNING_FLG FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE in_etl_control S SET s.txt_key_value = ( SELECT TXT_KEY_VALUE FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_PI_AOR_CYCLE_DATE'), s.dte_update_date = sysdate WHERE s.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_PI_AOR_MAX_CYCLE_DATE' AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_PI_AOR_CYCLE_DATE' AND NVL( DEC_ENFORCE_FLG,0 ) = 1 ); COMMIT;
